Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! Who are you?\NAnd I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought into\Nmy hospital, your name was Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:13.98,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,800)\pos(360,340)}House of Tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer! Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner! It's Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... I mean,\NI've brought Nina home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call the police from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't look like\Nthe police ever came...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Come back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You must come back to life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...\NYour favorite cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I... killed... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him... I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nina.\N- But that day, I killed my brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I brought him back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line has been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get\Naway from here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the police.\NWe received a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind,\Nwe'll have a look around inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right? Any injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank heavens.\NWe'll have help soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take care of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hear your stories\Ndown at headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the victims' daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that means\Nyou didn't see who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To think something like that could\Nhappen in such a peaceful town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from? China?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm Japanese.\NMy name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible experience for you\Nin such a faraway land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady... You're all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Heidelberg Police Department\Nis in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Mannheim Precinct\Nin the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder why they're taking us\Nto the next precinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be there in about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said they got a call...\NThey came because they got a call...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who could have called them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The phone line was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This car came without sirens blaring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would the police whisk away\Nthe people who discovered the bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without first securing the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, those police IDs\Nlooked authentic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It couldn't be that these men...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A roadblock?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're searching for\Na hit-and-run driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'd appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Detective Mesner\Nand Detective Muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... See you're doing your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on your way\Nback to headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got a new car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- What's going on?\N{\i0}- How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a junk heap in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you don't take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl says she doesn't feel well.\NCan we go out and get some air?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those two do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?\NAre they really detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what about that blood?\NWhose call did they receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They didn't even turn on their siren...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should we do? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you my name,\Nbut I didn't tell you that I was a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a grocery story nearby.\NI even found some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's bread, sausage and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had them pour\Nsome coffee into this thermos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not have any appetite,\Nbut you've got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you'd better change\Nyour clothes. You're freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of dead people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and I walked among them,\Njust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like... we were the only people\Nleft in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?\NCan't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We crossed the border...\NA man and and his wife cheered us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my brother said that\Nhe had a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The man and his wife died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone who's ever\Nbeen nice to us... all die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, I discovered\Nthe reason why... That rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about\NMr. and Mrs. Liebert, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother shot them...\NMy brother killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killed them all up till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I took the gun...\NI aimed it at my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed as he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"After you shoot me,\Nthrow the gun outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure you shoot me in the head."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot him like he said...\NI aimed for his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't saved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my mom and dad\Nwouldn't have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move from this place.\NI'll go to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the detectives last night\Nwere the real thing, that means that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,someone in the police department\Nis on Johan's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't just stay here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is trying to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hide\Nif someone comes looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat,\Ndrink some hot coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then sleep for a while...\NThat's how people go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive...\NYou must think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,100,,Don't you have any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,100,,Is there any connection to the string
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:18.96,Names2,,0,0,20,,{\fad(750,0)}Heidelberg Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,100,,of killings of middle-age couples\Nthroughout Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, we are putting all of\Nour resources into this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am not free to\Ndisclose any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have found that\NMr. and Mrs. Fortner have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is under investigation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was that newspaper reporter,\NMaurer, with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that Japanese guy\Nwho is said to have been with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese? He sounds suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that murder at Heidelberg Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurred at nearly the same time,\Nthe work of the same killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heidelberg Castle...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was killed, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we will keep you\Nabreast of the happenings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Please let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough for an article!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I appreciate the help offered\Nby the Mannheim police,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Detectives Mesner and Muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give us our orders.\NWe'll do all we can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the investigations\Ncoming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk about it inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're real...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those guys are really\Nwith the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heidelberg Post!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I can't hear you!\NThe editing room is in chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who are you?\N- we have to find that Japanese guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who was with Maurer!\NHe knows something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please quiet down! I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring an important witness\Nto your office at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not let the police know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!\NThis isn't a hoax, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can't trust the police,\Nthere's only the paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that can... keep Nina safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be in here\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're here from\Nthe federal police to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the killings of the middle-age couples,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have files on\Nthe killing at the castle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... Something was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The case you're looking at and\Nthis one happened at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be the same perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy... It looks like there are signs\Nthat his hands had been tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find rope or anything nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It had been removed\Nby the time the victim was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are four possible routes\Nof escape from the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had to consider whether\Nhe'd be hidden from sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how crowded the area was\Nwhere he'd come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the locations of the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, it's me... It's Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! You needn't hide anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Nina!! Nina!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... Was she taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just did what you\Nhad to do as a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the sandwiches\Nand get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to survive,\Nand save as many people as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina... What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you intend to try to\Nkill him again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought him back to life...\NThat monster... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought him back to life...
